title: Warhammer Fantasy Uniforms and Heraldry of the High Elves - 2012
description: This 72-page hardback book contains the full and glorious heraldry of the High Elves of Ulthuan - the defenders of the world. It comes with hundreds of full-colour illustrations of livery, shield designs and heraldic banners for this, the noblest and grandest of all the races of the world. Whether you're a painter or collector, this is a must-have reference book.
